README

# DEFAULT USER

Default user is `akamas` which is listed as a sudoer. You can freely use `sudo` command, as well as promoting to superuser with `sudo su -`

# OPERATING SYSTEM

Underlying system is Ubuntu. You can install missing packages with `sudo apt install <packagename>`

# PERSISTENT STORAGE

Folder named `/work` is persisted on a dedicated volume that will be remounted across restarts. You should store your important data files and/or config files and/or Akamas YAMLs there

# SSH ACCESS

You can also connect to this management pod via ssh protocol. The only user enabled for ssh connection is 'akamas'. The password is #PASSWORD#
